          "name": "순차 탐색 (Linear Search)",
          "time_complexity": "O(n)",
          "description": "처음부터 순서대로 탐색"
        },
        {
          "name": "이진 탐색 (Binary Search)",
          "time_complexity": "O(log n)",
          "description": "정렬된 배열에서 절반씩 범위를 줄여 탐색",
          "c_code": "int low=0, high=n-1;\nwhile(low <= high) {\n  int mid = (low+high)/2;\n  if(a[mid] == target) return mid;\n  else if(a[mid] < target) low = mid+1;\n  else high = mid-1;\n}"
        }
      ]
